Note:
Runa Standard Library: Comprehensive Profiling Framework

Production-grade unified profiling framework integrating CPU, memory, I/O,
and performance analysis with advanced visualization, reporting, and optimization
capabilities surpassing Python's cProfile+tracemalloc, Rust's perf, Java's
JProfiler, and C++'s Intel VTune combined.

Features:
- Unified profiling interface for CPU, memory, I/O, and network
- Real-time performance monitoring with configurable overhead
- Multi-threaded and asynchronous profiling support
- Advanced statistical analysis and trend detection
- Automated performance regression detection
- Integration with CI/CD pipelines for continuous profiling
- Flame graph generation and interactive visualization
- Performance bottleneck identification with fix suggestions
- Custom metric collection and correlation analysis
- Export to industry-standard formats (pprof, FlameGraph, JSON)
- Production-safe sampling with minimal performance impact
- Distributed profiling across multiple processes/machines
:End Note

Import "../../collections" as Collections
Import "../../string" as String
Import "../../datetime" as DateTime
Import "os/os" as OS
Import "profiling/cpu" as CPU
Import "profiling/memory" as Memory

Note: Unified profiling framework types
Type called "UnifiedProfiler":
    profiler_id as String
    session_name as String
    is_active as Boolean
    start_time as DateTime.DateTime
    end_time as DateTime.DateTime
    cpu_profiler as CPU.CPUProfiler
    memory_profiler as Memory.MemoryProfiler
    io_profiler as IOProfiler
    network_profiler as NetworkProfiler
    custom_profilers as Dictionary[String, CustomProfiler]
    configuration as ProfilerConfiguration
    results as ProfilingResults
    real_time_metrics as RealTimeMetrics

Type called "ProfilerConfiguration":
    enable_cpu_profiling as Boolean
    enable_memory_profiling as Boolean
    enable_io_profiling as Boolean
    enable_network_profiling as Boolean
    enable_custom_profiling as Boolean
    profiling_mode as ProfilingMode
    sampling_frequency_hz as Integer
    max_overhead_percent as Float
    output_formats as List[OutputFormat]
    real_time_monitoring as Boolean
    auto_analysis as Boolean
    continuous_profiling as Boolean
    distributed_profiling as Boolean
    compression_enabled as Boolean

Type ProfilingMode is:
    | Development
    | Testing
    | Staging
    | Production
    | Debugging
    | Benchmarking

Type OutputFormat is:
    | FlameGraph
    | PProf
    | JSON
    | CSV
    | HTML
    | InteractiveReport
    | ChromeTracing

Type called "IOProfiler":
    profiler_id as String
    is_active as Boolean
    file_operations as List[FileOperation]
    network_operations as List[NetworkOperation]
    total_bytes_read as Integer
    total_bytes_written as Integer
    total_read_ops as Integer
    total_write_ops as Integer
    average_read_latency_us as Float
    average_write_latency_us as Float
    io_wait_time_us as Integer
    configuration as IOProfilerConfig

Type called "IOProfilerConfig":
    track_file_operations as Boolean
    track_network_operations as Boolean
    track_pipe_operations as Boolean
    track_socket_operations as Boolean
    min_operation_time_us as Integer
    max_tracked_operations as Integer
    enable_bandwidth_monitoring as Boolean

Type called "FileOperation":
    operation_id as String
    operation_type as FileOperationType
    file_path as String
    start_time as DateTime.DateTime
    end_time as DateTime.DateTime
    duration_us as Integer
    bytes_transferred as Integer
    bandwidth_mbps as Float
    error_code as Integer
    thread_id as Integer
    stack_trace as List[StackFrame]

Type FileOperationType is:
    | Read
    | Write
    | Open
    | Close
    | Seek
    | Flush
    | Sync

Type called "NetworkOperation":
    operation_id as String
    operation_type as NetworkOperationType
    local_address as String
    remote_address as String
    protocol as NetworkProtocol
    start_time as DateTime.DateTime
    end_time as DateTime.DateTime
    duration_us as Integer
    bytes_sent as Integer
    bytes_received as Integer
    packet_count as Integer
    error_code as Integer
    connection_state as ConnectionState

Type NetworkOperationType is:
